    "description": "In <strong>Magic Research</strong>, you are the headmaster of a newly-created institution of Magic with one goal: to learn as much as possible about this power and get enough fame to be able to compete, and win, the prestigious competition of schools: the Tournament of Magic. But what will you discover along the way?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cast over a hundred different spells with various effects<br></li><li> Research magic in various magical schools to discover new, surprising ways to use this power<br></li><li> Accumulate resources and build the school campus<br></li><li> Manage a team of researchers and apprentices to lead your school to fame<br></li><li> Discover tons of hidden new features - when will you unlock the next one?<br></li><li> Find over six dozen secret Storylines with permanent, game-altering effects<br></li><li> Restart the game and make faster progress each time with retirement bonuses<br></li><li> Over 40 hours of addictive gameplay!</li></ul>",
